com.nokia.maps.kml

Interface Style


  • public interface Style
    This interface represents the <Style> tag from KML specification. A <Style> defines an addressable style group that can be referenced by <StyleMap> and <Feature> elements. Styles affect how Geometry is presented. Shared styles are collected in a <Document> and must have an id defined for them so that they can be referenced by the individual <Features> that use them.
